fields.name: Backpack
fields.description:
A timeless everyday backpack crafted from durable full-grain leather that develops a rich patina over time. Fits a 15" laptop, gym gear, and essentials without bulk. Approx. 20–22 L with internal zip pockets and padded laptop sleeve.

Material: leather shell, cotton canvas lining, steel hardware.

fields.description: Light, fast jump rope for conditioning and warm-ups. Textile-sheathed steel cable with aluminum handles. Length adjustable up to ~3 m with smooth bearings.

fields.name: Shaker
fields.description: Stainless-steel shaker that won’t retain flavors and seals tight in your bag. Food-grade steel with BPA-free gasket and wire whisk ball. Volume: 700 ml.

fields.description:

fields.name: Socks

fields.name: Sports bra

fields.name: Straps
